<section>
  <div class="px-8 md:px-12 py-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
    <div class="relative overflow-hidden">
      <div class="container flex flex-col justify-center overflow-hidden md:flex-row" x-data="{ testimonialActive: 1 }">
        <div>
          <div class="relative flex flex-col h-full text-left">
            <div class="relative z-10 h-full">
              <div class="pb-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
                <div x-show.immediate="testimonialActive === 1" style="display: none;">
                  <p class="font-medium leading-6 text-zinc-500 text-base text-balance flex gap-2 items-center text-center mx-auto">
                    Before working with Reignite Media, our Shopify store was barely making sales. Now, our revenue has skyrocketed, and we’re consistently seeing higher conversion rates. Best investment we’ve made.
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div x-show.immediate="testimonialActive === 2" style="display: none;">
                  <p class="font-medium leading-6 text-zinc-500 text-base text-balance flex gap-2 items-center text-center mx-auto max-w-md">
                    A complete game-changer for our brand. We struggled with slow load times and poor design. After the redesign and optimization, our bounce rate dropped, and our sales shot up. Highly recommend!
                  </p>
                </div>
                <div x-show.immediate="testimonialActive === 3" style="display: none;">
                  <p class="font-medium leading-6 text-zinc-500 text-base text-balance flex gap-2 items-center text-center mx-auto max-w-md">
                    We had traffic but no sales. This team transformed our store with a stunning design and optimized checkout flow. Now, we’re seeing real results—more customers, more sales, more growth!
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="flex items-center justify-center mt-6 lg:my-4">
                <button @click.prevent="testimonialActive = 1" class="inline-block mx-2 font-bold text-center rounded-full shadow-xs focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 size-12 opacity-50 bg-gradientdown" :class="{'size-12 opacity-50 bg-gradientdown ': testimonialActive != 1, 'opacity-100 bg-gradientdown text-white': testimonialActive == 1 }">
                  <img class="inline-block w-12 h-12 rounded-full grayscale border" src="/tonylea.jpg" alt="#" />
                </button>
                <button @click.prevent="testimonialActive = 2" class="inline-block mx-2 font-bold text-center rounded-full shadow-xs focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 opacity-100 bg-gradientdown text-white" :class="{'size-12 opacity-50 bg-gradientdown ': testimonialActive != 2, 'opacity-100 bg-gradientdown text-white': testimonialActive == 2 }">
                  <img class="inline-block w-12 h-12 rounded-full grayscale border" src="/volkan.jpg" alt="#" />
                </button>
                <button @click.prevent="testimonialActive = 3" class="inline-block mx-2 font-bold text-center rounded-full shadow-xs focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 opacity-100 bg-gradientdown text-white" :class="{'size-12 opacity-50 bg-gradientdown ': testimonialActive != 3, 'opacity-100 bg-gradientdown text-white': testimonialActive == 3 }">
                  <img class="inline-block w-12 h-12 rounded-full grayscale border" src="/daniel.png" alt="#" />
                </button>
              </div>
              <div class="flex justify-center px-4 pt-4 pb-6 md:py-6">
                <div class="text-center" x-show="testimonialActive == 1" style="display: none;">
                  <h2 class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-medium lg:text-base">James R.</h2>
                  <a href="#" class="text-xs text-zinc-500">Founder of Kohinoor</a>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center" x-show="testimonialActive == 2" style="display: none;">
                  <h2 class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-medium lg:text-base">Samantha L.</h2>
                  <a href="#" class="text-xs text-zinc-500">CEO of Ecobeaver</a>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center" x-show="testimonialActive == 3" style="display: none;">
                  <h2 class="text-zinc-500 text-sm font-medium lg:text-base">Daniel M.</h2>
                  <a href="#" class="text-xs text-zinc-500">Co-Founder of FitFuel</a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
